Installation Instructions:

1. Install Following Plugins in WP:

Check & Log Email
Insert PHP Code Snippet
WP Data Access
WP Mail SMTP


2. Create below folders in WP Root:
/wp-content/uploads/images/

3. Create php Insert code snippets as per the scripts

4. Create DB datatable

5. Insert records in datatables

6. Configure WP Mail SMTP configuration

7. Create appropriate pages

